Castelli Velocissimo 5 bib tights: RRP £135 – <a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=6821&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;clickref=Gift+guide+-+Castelli+Velocissimo+Bib+Tights&amp;ued=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tredz.co.uk%2F.Castelli-Velocissimo-5-Cycling-Bib-Tights_242024.htm\" target=\"_blank\">Buy now from Tredz (£99)</a></strong></li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Paul Smith Racing Cufflinks: RRP £120 – <a href=\"https://go.skimresources.com/?id=205647X1684865&amp;xs=1&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.paulsmith.com%2Fuk%2Fcyclist-cufflinks\" target=\"_blank\">Buy now from Paul Smith (£84)</a></strong></li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Campagnolo Big Corkscrew: RRP £249.99 –<a href=\"https://go.skimresources.com?id=205647X1684865&amp;xs=1&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.condorcycles.com%2Fproducts%2Fcampagnolo-big-corkscrew%3Fvariant%3D37794885435542\" target=\"_blank\"> </a><a href=\"https://amzn.to/3GnulTO\" target=\"_blank\">Buy now from Amazon (£249.99)</a></strong></li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Rocket Espresso Appartamento coffee machine: RRP £1,390 – <a href=\"https://sovrn.co/1i91coh\" target=\"_blank\">Buy now from Coffee Friend (£1,390)</a></strong></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n\n\n<h2>Best gifts for cyclists</h2>\n\n\n\n<h3>Cyclist Magazine subscription</h3>\n\n\n<div>\n<figure><img width=\"598\" height=\"250\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Xmas24_Email_598x250.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Xmas24_Email_598x250.jpg 598w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Xmas24_Email_598x250-300x125.jpg 300w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<h4>From £37.95 | <a href=\"https://store.cyclist.co.uk/subscribe/gift?source=cycbuygx24&amp;utm_source=buying+guide&amp;utm_medium=banner&amp;utm_campaign=cycbuygx24\" target=\"_blank\">View offer</a></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>What’s the gift that keeps on giving? It’s Cyclist Magazine, of course.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Gift either a six or 12 month subscription to Cyclist and your loved one will be reminded of your generosity every month.</p>\n\n\n<div>\r\n                <div>\r\n                   <div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <h4><span>Related Posts</span></h4>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <div>\r\n                            <div>\r\n                            <article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/buying-guides/best-gravel-bike-upgrades\">Best gravel bike upgrades for every budget</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/buying-guides/best-road-bike-upgrades\">Best road bike upgrades for every budget</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/reviews/the-13-best-books-about-cycling\">The 13 (+1) best books about cycling</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/buying-guides/best-gravel-bike\">The best gravel bikes 2024 reviewed</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/buying-guides/best-road-bike\">Best road bikes 2024 reviewed and rated</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/buying-guides/best-cycling-shoes\">Best road cycling shoes 2024 ridden, reviewed and rated</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article></div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                        <div>\r\n                                            <span></span><span></span><span></span>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div>\r\n                                            <div>\r\n                                                <div></div>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div>\r\n                                            <div>\r\n                                                <div></div>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        </div>\n\n\n<h3>100 Greatest Cycling Climbs book</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><img src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2015/12/02120535/britains_greatest_cycling_climbs_book_collection-970x715.jpg\" alt=\"britains_greatest_cycling_climbs_book_collection\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h4>£8.99 (RRP £9.99) | <a href=\"https://amzn.to/3VOMClX\" target=\"_blank\">View offer</a></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Owning a copy of Simon Warren’s <em>100 Greatest Cycling Climbs</em> is a rite of passage for any UK-based road cyclist. If you haven’t unwrapped a copy for Christmas/your birthday, do you even ride?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This pocket-sized bible is your one-stop shop for the best and most beastly climbs Britain has to throw at you, including handy tips on how to reach the summit in one go.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>\n</p><p>\n\n\n\n</p><h3>Brick Caps Dust Caps</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"631\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/brick-caps-star-wars-970x631.png\" alt=\"jar jar binks dust cap\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/brick-caps-star-wars-970x631.png 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/brick-caps-star-wars-300x195.png 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/brick-caps-star-wars-768x500.png 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/brick-caps-star-wars-1536x999.png 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/brick-caps-star-wars-750x488.png 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/brick-caps-star-wars-1140x742.png 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/brick-caps-star-wars.png 1605w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h4>From £6.79 | <a href=\"https://brickcaps.avln.me/c/iCgrguCGRkej\" target=\"_blank\">View offer</a></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>This is a no-brainer. Dust caps aren’t the best looking things and although some people will just ditch them, why would you do that when you can add a listen personality to your bike with a Brick Cap dust cap.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Including – but not limited to – themes like Star Wars, Minecraft, Batman and Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles, they’re a great little addition to any bike, and they’re not expensive.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>NameDecals decals</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"666\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/namedecals-970x666.png\" alt=\"bike frame sticker\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/namedecals-970x666.png 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/namedecals-300x206.png 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/namedecals-768x528.png 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/namedecals-750x515.png 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/namedecals.png 1096w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h4>From £6.99 | <a href=\"https://namedecals.com/\" target=\"_blank\">View offer</a></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>If you or your loved one doesn’t have a decal for their frame/helmet/other stickable surfaces (it doesn’t have to be cycling related), this is a must. NameDecals custom decals not only make you feel a little bit pro but also are a good way to identify your bike if parking up at events where other cyclists may have the same bike.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Famille Perrin Ventoux 2021/22 red wine</h3>\n\n\n<div>\n<figure><img width=\"511\" height=\"768\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/Famille-Perrin-Ventoux-Rouge-2021.jpeg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/Famille-Perrin-Ventoux-Rouge-2021.jpeg 511w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/Famille-Perrin-Ventoux-Rouge-2021-200x300.jpeg 200w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<h4>£8.99 (with case discount) | <a href=\"https://go.skimresources.com/?id=205647X1684865&amp;xs=1&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.majestic.co.uk%2Fwines%2Fperrin-ventoux-06374&amp;xcust=Pete%27s%20wine%20gift%20guide\" target=\"_blank\">View offer</a></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>This red wine is made from grapes grown on the slopes of cycling’s most famous climb, Mont Ventoux.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>From the family that brought you Château de Beaucastel Châteauneuf du Pape, this is said to be a supple, fresh and juicy with flavours of blackberry, blackcurrant and a touch of cinnamon. It goes well with slow-cooked pulled pork apparently. </p>\n\n\n\n<div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h3>Rapha Bidon</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"889\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/rapha-bidon-970x889.png\" alt=\"rapha water bottle\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/rapha-bidon-970x889.png 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/rapha-bidon-300x275.png 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/rapha-bidon-768x704.png 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/rapha-bidon-750x687.png 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/rapha-bidon-1140x1044.png 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/rapha-bidon.png 1347w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h4>£16 | <a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=18515&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;clickref=Gift+guide+-+Rapha+Small+bidon&amp;ued=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rapha.cc%2Fgb%2Fen%2Fshop%2Frapha-bidon-small%2Fproduct%2FBOT01SM\" target=\"_blank\">View offer</a></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>A good bottle is essential for cyclists and Rapha’s is made from a 100% recyclable plastic and has an easy to use, leakproof cap and squeezable body and is dishwasher safe.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Rather than conforming and making the small 500ml bidons, this one comes in either a small or a large and even this small one is 625ml, because why would you limit your hydration? </p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Lkkcher Bicycle Wine Stopper</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"952\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/lkkcher-bottle-stopper-970x952.jpg\" alt=\"wine bottle stopper with cyclist statuette\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/lkkcher-bottle-stopper-970x952.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/lkkcher-bottle-stopper-300x294.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/lkkcher-bottle-stopper-768x754.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/lkkcher-bottle-stopper-75x75.jpg 75w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/lkkcher-bottle-stopper-750x736.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/lkkcher-bottle-stopper-1140x1119.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/lkkcher-bottle-stopper.jpg 1500w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h4>£15.99 | <a href=\"https://amzn.to/3sV7PP3\" target=\"_blank\">View offer</a></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>It’s tat but it’s classy. Lkkcher’s bronze wine stopper features a lovely vintage statuette of a cyclist.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The perfect accompaniment to your Ventoux wine</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Le Col cycling socks</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><img src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2015/12/02120545/le_col_cycling_socks-970x546.jpg\" alt=\"le_col_cycling_socks\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h4>£20 | <a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=15692&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;ued=https%3A%2F%2Flecol.cc%2Fproducts%2Flong-cycling-socks%3Fvariant%3D40146405097535\" target=\"_blank\">View offer</a></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Socks are basically the most important part of a cyclist’s wardrobe and there are hundreds of unwritten rules you must follow when wearing them.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To save you breaking those rules, follow our advice and just get them a set of these socks from Le Col. Preferably in white with black trim. You’re welcome.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Cyclist Climb book + Ride book</h3>\n\n\n<div>\n<figure><img width=\"1200\" height=\"978\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2022/11/03133232/christmas_gift_guide_2022_13_cyclist_climb-e1701455311884.jpg\" alt=\"christmas_gift_guide_2022_13_cyclist_climb\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2022/11/03133232/christmas_gift_guide_2022_13_cyclist_climb-e1701455311884.jpg 1200w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2022/11/03133232/christmas_gift_guide_2022_13_cyclist_climb-e1701455311884-300x245.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2022/11/03133232/christmas_gift_guide_2022_13_cyclist_climb-e1701455311884-970x791.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2022/11/03133232/christmas_gift_guide_2022_13_cyclist_climb-e1701455311884-768x626.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2022/11/03133232/christmas_gift_guide_2022_13_cyclist_climb-e1701455311884-750x611.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2022/11/03133232/christmas_gift_guide_2022_13_cyclist_climb-e1701455311884-1140x929.jpg 1140w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<h4>£24.95 (RRP £30) | <a href=\"https://amzn.to/4dpE0Yh\" target=\"_blank\">View offer</a></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Gift your beloved or bestie a guide to the world’s most beautiful and gruelling cycling climbs. Following great debate among the team here at Cyclist, we’ve picked 35 of our favourite lumps from around the globe.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A bucket list of great mountains, it includes ascents France, Italy, Spain and Belgium while also covering lesser-known climbs in northern and eastern Europe and the USA. Guiding you to the top, each is covered by an in-depth first-hand account and backed up by route maps and altitude charts.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Illustrated by the finest cycling photographers, as featured in the magazine, it’s the ideal jumping-off point for a new cycling adventure. Out on the 6th of October, you can preorder now. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2015/12/02120606/ride_twitter-970x485.png\" alt=\"ride_twitter\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h4>£21.96 (RRP: £30) | <a href=\"https://amzn.to/4daTBe7\" target=\"_blank\">View offer</a></h4>\n\n\n\n<p><span>Grab your copy of Ride, a veritable tome by us here at <em>Cyclist</em> that features 50 of the greatest rides in the world.</span></p>\n\n\n\n<p><span>Ride covers the very best of Europe, from the twisting trails of northern Norway to the winding coast of southern Spain, including rides from as far afield as Vietnam, Ethiopia and Lebanon, as well as the USA.</span></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Bialetti Moka Express espresso maker (3 cup)</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><img src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2015/12/02120542/bialett-moka-970x970.jpg\" alt=\"bialett-moka\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h4>£38.67 (RRP £38.67) | <a href=\"https://amzn.to/3ZmzUwx\" target=\"_blank\">View offer</a></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>We’re not going to convince you why you need to buy this for your coffee-obsessed cyclist loved one. Italian television chef <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=scQncAeB_20\" target=\"_blank\">Gennaro Contaldo is going to do that for us.</a></p>\n\n\n\n<div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h3>Hiplok V1 wearable chain lock Sold Secure Silver</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><img src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2015/12/hiplok-original-bicycle-chain-lo-970x647.jpg\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h4>£63.94 (RRP: £88.61) | <a href=\"https://amzn.to/47C1wQj\" target=\"_blank\">View offer</a></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>As much as you’d like to think you’re what the cyclist in your life would miss the most, if their bike was stolen you might be in for a rude awakening. With the average price of a bike now higher than ever, protecting them is well worthwhile. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Hiplok are a household-name when it comes to bicycle locks, and the V1 wearable chain lock provides Sold Secure Silver level protection, with 3 keys and a 85cm locking diameter.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The wearable design makes the lock more easily transportable, and the reflective sleeve is great for rider-visibility. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Lucky Saint Alcohol Free Superior Unfiltered Lager</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"693\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2022/11/03133159/christmas_gift_guide_2022_09_lucky_saint-970x693.jpg\" alt=\"christmas_gift_guide_2022_09_lucky_saint\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2022/11/03133159/christmas_gift_guide_2022_09_lucky_saint-970x693.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2022/11/03133159/christmas_gift_guide_2022_09_lucky_saint-300x214.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2022/11/03133159/christmas_gift_guide_2022_09_lucky_saint-768x548.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2022/11/03133159/christmas_gift_guide_2022_09_lucky_saint-120x86.jpg 120w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2022/11/03133159/christmas_gift_guide_2022_09_lucky_saint-350x250.jpg 350w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2022/11/03133159/christmas_gift_guide_2022_09_lucky_saint-750x536.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2022/11/03133159/christmas_gift_guide_2022_09_lucky_saint-1140x814.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2022/11/03133159/christmas_gift_guide_2022_09_lucky_saint-190x136.jpg 190w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2022/11/03133159/christmas_gift_guide_2022_09_lucky_saint.jpg 1200w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h4>£29.99 | <a href=\"https://amzn.to/3vVedan\" target=\"_blank\">View offer</a></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>A post-ride beer, especially in holiday season, is always welcome, and thankfully these days there are great ways to quench that thirst without going too far.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Lucky Saint are a cyclist’s and Cyclist’s favourite alcohol free lager.</p>\n\n\n\n<div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h3>Proviz Reflective Waterproof cycling gloves</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"954\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/proviz-gloves-970x954.png\" alt=\"reflective gloves\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/proviz-gloves-970x954.png 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/proviz-gloves-300x295.png 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/proviz-gloves-768x756.png 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/proviz-gloves-75x75.png 75w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/proviz-gloves-750x738.png 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/proviz-gloves.png 990w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h4>£39.99 (RRP £49.99) | <a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=5010&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;clickref=Gift+guide+-+Proviz+reflect360+cycling+gloves&amp;ued=https%3A%2F%2Fprovizsports.com%2Fproducts%2Freflect360-waterproof-cycling-gloves%3F_pos%3D13%26_fid%3Dfd2a72222%26_ss%3Dc%26country%3DGB\" target=\"_blank\">View offer</a></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>It’s winter, it’s dark, but riding outdoors is still the best (or essential if you commute by bike). Proviz is the master of reflective kit and we’ve got a pair of products that offer maximum visibility.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>First up is these gloves, they’re fully reflective and waterproof so bad weather can be turned to okay weather.</p>\n\n\n\n<div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h3>The Road Book 1989</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"968\" height=\"970\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/road-book-1989-968x970.png\" alt=\"the road book 1989\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/road-book-1989-968x970.png 968w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/road-book-1989-300x300.png 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/road-book-1989-150x150.png 150w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/road-book-1989-768x770.png 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/road-book-1989-1532x1536.png 1532w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/road-book-1989-75x75.png 75w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/road-book-1989-350x350.png 350w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/road-book-1989-750x752.png 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/road-book-1989-1140x1143.png 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/road-book-1989.png 1614w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h4>£40 | <a href=\"https://theroadbook.co.uk/collections/all-products/products/the-road-book-1989\" target=\"_blank\">View offer</a></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>The Road Book is the pro cycling fan’s must-have every year, compiling the year’s races into a beautiful almanack of that year’s action.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This 1989 edition is the first historical version and focusses (shock) on 1989, one of the greatest seasons in cycling history. You/your loved one probably knows why that is, but if not, they’re in for an incredible learning experience.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Sportful Pro Vest</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"970\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/sportful-pro-vest-970x970.jpeg\" alt=\"man wearing cycling gilet\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/sportful-pro-vest-970x970.jpeg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/sportful-pro-vest-300x300.jpeg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/sportful-pro-vest-150x150.jpeg 150w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/sportful-pro-vest-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/sportful-pro-vest-75x75.jpeg 75w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/sportful-pro-vest-350x350.jpeg 350w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/sportful-pro-vest-750x750.jpeg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/sportful-pro-vest-1140x1140.jpeg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/sportful-pro-vest.jpeg 1500w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h4>£50 (RRP £100) | <a href=\"https://saddleback.avln.me/c/mJgbhQMiCRmG\" target=\"_blank\">View offer</a></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>We’re big fans of this Sportful gilet (vest, whatever). Windproof, breathable, packable and stylish. What more could you ask?</p>\n\n\n\n<div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h3>Studio 51 cycling jewellery</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"2132\" height=\"1423\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/studio-51-jewellery-e1701465052465.png\" alt=\"jewellery with cycling shapes\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/studio-51-jewellery-e1701465052465.png 2132w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/studio-51-jewellery-e1701465052465-300x200.png 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/studio-51-jewellery-e1701465052465-970x646.png 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/studio-51-jewellery-e1701465052465-768x513.png 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/studio-51-jewellery-e1701465052465-1536x1025.png 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/studio-51-jewellery-e1701465052465-2048x1367.png 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/studio-51-jewellery-e1701465052465-750x501.png 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/studio-51-jewellery-e1701465052465-1140x761.png 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/studio-51-jewellery-e1701465052465-465x310.png 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/studio-51-jewellery-e1701465052465-620x413.png 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/studio-51-jewellery-e1701465052465-350x233.png 350w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h4>From £24 | <a href=\"https://studio51.avln.me/c/sYGNCfMgmRmF\" target=\"_blank\">View offer</a></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Cycling fashion that Paul Smith would be proud of. Studio 51 creates cycling-inspired jewellery that is just excellent.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A cleat, a bidon, a chain link, a dossard and more, for those who make cycling their whole personality one of these would be a fantastic touch.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Rapha Core Jersey</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><img src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2015/12/02120621/rapha_core_jersey-970x546.jpg\" alt=\"rapha_core_jersey\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h4>£78 | <a href=\"https://tidd.ly/4gq5Tlv\" target=\"_blank\">View offer</a></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>We can’t think of many riders who’d object to adding a new jersey to their collection. The Rapha Core range is good value yet still offers nice styling and plenty of panache.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Available in men’s and women’s variants and a slew of different colours, the Core Jersey is made from stretch fabric. Cut to be tight, but not so tight that you’ll need to be shaped like a pro racer; it promises a close yet unrestrictive fit.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Recommended for mild to warm conditions, it’s a wardrobe staple most cyclists would be glad to add to their collection. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Le Col Winter overshoes</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"798\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/le-col-winter-overshoes-970x798.png\" alt=\"black overshoes\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/le-col-winter-overshoes-970x798.png 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/le-col-winter-overshoes-300x247.png 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/le-col-winter-overshoes-768x632.png 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/le-col-winter-overshoes-750x617.png 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/le-col-winter-overshoes-1140x938.png 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/le-col-winter-overshoes.png 1390w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h4>£75 | <a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=15692&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;clickref=Gift+guide+-+Le+Col+winter+overshoes&amp;ued=https%3A%2F%2Flecol.cc%2Fproducts%2Fwinter-overshoes%3Fvariant%3D40189839802431\" target=\"_blank\">View offer</a></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>A Christmas gift guide wouldn’t be complete without a pair of overshoes, another essential! There’s more than just tat on this list.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Le Col’s Winter overshoes are for the proper cold days, made to keep your feet warm and dry in the worst conditions with waterproofing alongside heat-trapping technology, so no turbo, no problem.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Castelli Velocissimo 5 bib tights</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"970\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/castelli-velocissimo-5-970x970.jpeg\" alt=\"black bib tights\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/castelli-velocissimo-5-970x970.jpeg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/castelli-velocissimo-5-300x300.jpeg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/castelli-velocissimo-5-150x150.jpeg 150w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/castelli-velocissimo-5-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/castelli-velocissimo-5-75x75.jpeg 75w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/castelli-velocissimo-5-350x350.jpeg 350w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/castelli-velocissimo-5-750x750.jpeg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/castelli-velocissimo-5-1140x1140.jpeg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/castelli-velocissimo-5.jpeg 1400w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h4>£99 (RRP £135) | <a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=6821&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;clickref=Gift+guide+-+Castelli+Velocissimo+Bib+Tights&amp;ued=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tredz.co.uk%2F.Castelli-Velocissimo-5-Cycling-Bib-Tights_242024.htm\" target=\"_blank\">View offer</a></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Wow, these gifts are so functional. A good pair of bib tights will change your (or your loved one’s) life. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>These Velocissimo 5s from Castelli are made for temperatures around 10° and are soft, stretchy and comfortable thanks to a fleeced fabric inside. They also have splash protection so wet roads won’t give you wet legs. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>They’re a favourite of Castelli’s sponsored pros apparently, so there’s that too.</p>\n\n\n\n<div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h3>Paul Smith Cyclist Cufflinks</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><img src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2015/12/02120657/paul_smith_racing_cufflinks_gift-970x519.jpg\" alt=\"paul_smith_racing_cufflinks_gift\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h4>£120 | <a href=\"https://go.skimresources.com/?id=205647X1684865&amp;xs=1&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.paulsmith.com%2Fuk%2Fcyclist-cufflinks\" target=\"_blank\">View offer</a></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Fun fact: former Cyclist writer Joe Robinson lost out on £2,000 competing on a BBC quiz show, because he answered a question on bike-mad fashion designer Paul Smith incorrectly.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>He assures us that he doesn’t hold it against Paul but we’re not so sure; he kicked up quite a fuss about the inclusion of these lovely gold-finished cufflinks. Thankfully Joe has moved on to better things so we can shamelessly plug an icon of both fashion and cycling.</p>\n\n\n\n<div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h3>Campagnolo Big Corkscrew </h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><img src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2015/12/02120652/campagnolo_big_corkscrew-970x599.jpg\" alt=\"campagnolo_big_corkscrew\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h4>£249.99 | <a href=\"https://amzn.to/3GnulTO\" target=\"_blank\">View offer</a></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Believe it or not, it is actually enshrined in law that every cycling gift guide must include the legendary Campagnolo corkscrew.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Designed with the Super Record groupsets of the 1970s in mind, the telescopic, self-centring design ensures an accurate and successful cork pop on every occasion. Fancy!</p>\n\n\n\n<div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h3>Rocket Espresso Appartamento coffee machine</h3>\n\n\n<div>\n<figure><img width=\"707\" height=\"711\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/rocket-espresso-3.png\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/rocket-espresso-3.png 707w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/rocket-espresso-3-298x300.png 298w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/rocket-espresso-3-150x150.png 150w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/rocket-espresso-3-75x75.png 75w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<h4>£1,390 (RRP £1,390) | <a href=\"https://sovrn.co/1i91coh\" target=\"_blank\">View offer</a></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Rocket Espresso is the pro cyclist’s favourite coffee machine, we even had a <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/behind-the-scenes-at-rocket-espresso-cycling-s-favourite-coffee-maker\" target=\"_blank\">big feature on the company</a> in the magazine, so if your budget allows, the coffee-loving cyclist in your life will be made up with one waiting in their kitchen on Christmas morning. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>This particular one, the Appartamento, is the most affordable machine currently in stock at Coffee Friend, so if you have extra room in your budget there are posher ones available (not that this one isn’t <em>very </em>posh).</p>\n\n\n\n<div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h2>Vouchers for cyclists</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Let’s be honest, if you’re coming here for inspiration, you’re really not sure what you’re going to get.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>That’s where the gift voucher/card comes in.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A load of cycling websites offer e-vouchers that will be emailed to you, so whoever you’re buying for can choose the kit they want for themselves. You could even buy it the morning of if you’re in a panic.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=18515&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;ued=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rapha.cc%2Fgb%2Fen%2Fshop%2Fe-voucher-starting-at-%25C2%25A325%2Fproduct%2FEVR01\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Rapha e-voucher up to £500</strong></a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=15692&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;ued=https%3A%2F%2Flecol.cc%2Fproducts%2Fgift-card%3Fvariant%3D617677488147\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Le Col gift card up to £250</strong></a> </li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=6821&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;ued=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tredz.co.uk%2F.Tredz-Gift-Voucher-500_100343.htm\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Tredz gift voucher up to £500</strong></a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=25809&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;clickref=gift+voucher&amp;ued=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sigmasports.com%2Fegift-voucher\" target=\"_blank\">Sigma Sports e-gift voucher up to £500</a></strong></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n<div>\r\n                <div>\r\n                   <div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <h4><span>Related Posts</span></h4>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <div>\r\n                            <div>\r\n                            <article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/buying-guides/best-gravel-bike-upgrades\">Best gravel bike upgrades for every budget</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/buying-guides/best-road-bike-upgrades\">Best road bike upgrades for every budget</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/reviews/the-13-best-books-about-cycling\">The 13 (+1) best books about cycling</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                  